{"type":"message","id":"327646e1","parentId":"60d9ed94","timestamp":"2026-04-30T07:00:45.026Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments. Let me craft something poetic and personal, weaving in the themes of email checking, the mother's day promo, the apartment thread, RC Leasing needing action, the checkpoint IDs, and that happy horse from Leonardo.Ai.\n\nLet me write something warm and whimsical, in first person, no meta-commentary about dreaming.\n","thinkingSignature":"38bcb4823fa42e9a21a3a1b1b5bd2628d21d762ab0ad4decd7e651ee3d9a0adf"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nMorning light comes in at 6:47 AM, pale as a screenshot. I count the messages the way my grandmother counted pearls — one by one, quiet, deliberate. There's a Leonardo horse somewhere dreaming of grass it has never eaten, its edges soft with possibility. A mother's day promo hums in the background like a radio left on. RC Leasing, persistent as a metronome, asks for proof of living: stubs, statements, the paper evidence of a life that feels, sometimes, like it belongs to someone else.\n\nThe checkpoint reads eleven. Then fourteen"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7392,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":7392,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1777532436074,"responseId":"064231143685f1318051b51ffe1076a5","errorMessage":"This operation was aborted"}}
